data.description:
I have eaten Greek food all my life. My father was a fantastic chef who taught us all
about food, quality and eating ethically grown produce. Cooking Greek comes naturally
to me. For me, Greek food is the best in the world. Not just because they use fresh
vegetables and local meat and fish and because they don't over-power with spices, but
because it comes with the whole package of wine, ouzo and conversation that can go all
afternoon or all night long. As anyone who has visited Greece will tell you, eating and
drinking is a way of life whether you are having lunch on a beach or dinner at a
taverna. I am bringing this to you, hearty food using first class quality seasonal
produce, from farms across the UK, to produce the tastiest Greek Menu.
data.name: Taste of Greece
